    dc:description "FIGURE 3. a – f, T. bivittata; g – l, T. simplicis. a, g, male stridulatory file on underside of left tegmen; b, i, male abdominal apex in lateral view; c, j, male subgenital plate in ventral view; d, h, male cerci in dorsal view; e, k, female abdominal apex in lateral view; f, l, female subgenital plate in ventral view." ;
