<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.193110>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. a, d – j, T. quadridens; b, g – k, T. spinicaudata; c, l – q, T. parapentagona Liu & Kang, sp. n.. a – c, male stridulatory file on underside of left tegmen; d, g, l, male abdominal apex in lateral view; e, male abdominal apex in ventral view; i, o, male subgenital plate in ventral view; f, m, male tenth abdominal tergum in dorsal view; h, n, male cerci in dorsal view; j, p, female abdominal apex in lateral view; k, q, female subgenital plate in ventral view." ;
